Microscopic Life in Sphagnum</p>

<p>Sphagnum moss is often used in crafting and gardening as a planting medium (for example, for orchids), for lining baskets, for seed starting, or for decorative purposes, such as the Japanese moss balls called <em>kokedama</em>.</p>

<p><img src="kokedama%20jpg.jpg" alt="" />
